==English==
===Etymology===
From Late Latin ''[[#Latin|paragoge]]'', from Greek ''[[παραγωγη]]'' ‘derivation, addition’.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/pærəˈgəʊʤi/}}

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun|-}}

#{{grammar}} The addition of a [[sound]], [[syllable]] or letter to the end of a [[word]], either through natural development or as a grammatical function.
#: ''example'': [[without]] + [[-en]] = [[withouten]]

